    "This is however still worse than the Dolly v1 version with 6B parameters, which is also based on GPT-J and scored 31.8%.",
    "Instruct GPT-J further pushes this score to 39.1%.Surprisingly, Dolly v2 does not score better than v1 but only 30.0%, although it has twice the number of parameters.",
